et-mehra-2024-6%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Congress-Trinamool%20Deadlock%20Over%20Speaker%20Election%20Continues%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWest%20Bengal%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerje's%20Trinamool%20Congress%20has%20remained%20the%20shaky%20spot%20in%20the%20united%20Opposition%20front%20over%20the%20election%20of%20the%20Speaker.%20The%20party%2C%20which%20started%20the%20day%20with%20the%20complaint%20that%20they%20were%20not%20consulted%20about%20fielding%20a%20candidate%2C%20ended%20it%20by%20expressing%20its%20disapproval%20of%20the%20Congress%20decision%20and%20keeping%20the%20alliance%20on%20tenterhooks%20over%20its%20support%20to%20K%20Suresh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20meeting%20of%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20at%20Congress%20chief%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge's%20house%20on%20Tuesday%20evening%2C%20Trinamool%20expressed%20its%20reservation%20about%20the%20decision%20to%20go%20for%20a%20contest%2C%20sources%20said.%20On%20whether%20it%20would%20support%20K%20Suresh%20against%20the%20BJP%20candidate%20Om%20Birla%2C%20the%20party%20said%20they%20would%20convey%20their%20decision%20by%209%20am%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20the%20party%20had%20argued%20that%20some%20of%20their%20members%20could%20not%20take%20oath%20and%20some%20Opposition%20MPs%20are%20in%20jail.%20So%20a%20contest%20at%20this%20point%20will%20only%20put%20then%20NDA%20strength%20on%20display.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20Congress's%20eleventh-hour%20snap%20decision%20to%20field%20Mr%20Suresh%20and%20force%20a%20contest%2C%20had%20got%20it%20on%20the%20wrong%20side%20of%20Trinamool%2C%20which%20called%20the%20move%20%26quot%3Bunilateral%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20hours%20and%20explanations%20later%2C%20the%20party%20thawed%20and%20attended%20the%20Opposition%20meet%20--%20only%20to%20express%20its%20reservations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAhead%20of%20the%20meeting%2C%20Congress's%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20had%20spoken%20to%20Trinamool's%20second-in-command%20Abhishek%20Banerjee%20and%20Mr%20Suresh%20had%20called%20the%20party%20to%20seek%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20said%20there%20was%20no%20time%20for%20consultation%20as%20they%20had%20decided%20to%20field%20a%20candidate%20just%2010%20minutes%20before%20the%20deadline.%20The%20part%20was%20irked%20by%20the%20BJP%20refusal%20to%20give%20the%20Opposition%20the%20post%20of%20the%20Deputy%20Speaker%2C%20or%20admit%20their%20claim%20to%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20morning%2C%20the%20government%2C%20while%20seeking%20consensus%20for%20Om%20Birla%2C%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20they%20were%20not%20considering%20a%20Deputy%20Speaker%20post%20for%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress's%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20who%20has%20accepted%20the%20responsibility%20of%20being%20the%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BRajnath%20Singh%20called%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20and%20asked%20him%20to%20extend%20support...%20entire%20Opposition%20said%20we%20will%20support%20but%20convention%20is%20Deputy%20Speaker%20should%20be%20from%20our%20side.%20Rajnath%20Singh%20said%20he%20would%20call%20back...%20but%20he%20has%20not%20yet...PM%20is%20asking%20for%20cooperation%20but%20our%20leader%20is%20getting%20insulted.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Trinamool%20--%20which%20never%20had%20the%20best%20of%20relations%20with%20the%20Congress%20--%20had%20put%20its%20membership%20from%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20on%20hold%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20polls%20after%20a%20dispute%20over%20seat%20sharing%20in%20Bengal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20election%2C%20they%20came%20back%20to%20the%20fold%20and%20today%20was%20the%20first%20day%20after%20the%20results%2C%20when%20unease%20crept%20into%20the%20alliance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20not%20Trinamool%20alone.%20Sources%20said%20after%20the%20meeting%20that%20alliance%20leaders%20had%20underscored%20that%20they%20were%20not%20informed%20about%20Sonia%20Gandhi's