0f15435159aef229d0%26postID%3D667b2f1a85b49b35b28073f1%26postSlug%3Dgay-professional-wrestler-princey-phanesse-were-here-hbo-interview-2024-6%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.max.com%252F%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EMax%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%20The%20conversation%20was%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20first%20got%20into%20wrestling%20when%20I%20was%20in%20diapers.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20grew%20up%20the%20youngest%20of%20two%20older%20brothers.%20Wrestling%20has%20always%20been%20around%20in%20my%20life%2C%20ever%20since%20I%20was%20a%20baby.%20I%20remember%20having%20the%20action%20figures%2C%20the%20video%20games%2C%20and%20everything%20%E2%80%94%20I%20was%20just%20obsessed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20kind%20of%20lost%20interest%20a%20little%20bit%20growing%20up%2C%20and%20then%20I%20got%20back%20into%20it%20when%20I%20was%2018%20or%20so.%20My%20mom%20passed%20away%20when%20I%20was%2023%20and%20I%20was%20just%20kind%20of%20depressed%2C%20sad%2C%20and%20I%20was%20flipping%20through%20the%20channels%20and%20saw%20that%20%26quot%3BMonday%20Night%20RAW%26quot%3B%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ewas%20on.%20I%20was%20with%20some%20friends%20watching%20it%20and%20something%20just%20clicked%20in%20my%20head%3A%20%26quot%3BWhy%20aren't%20I%20doing%20this%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGrowing%20up%20in%20Murfreesboro%2C%20being%20this%20out%2C%20proud%20gay%20Black%20man%20was%20kind%20of%20just%20frowned%20upon.%20To%20protect%20myself%20from%20getting%20insulted%20or%20attacked%2C%20I%20kind%20of%20just%20covered%20it%20up.%20And%20Princey%20was%20just%20kind%20of%20this%20quiet%20individual%20who%20never%20really%20went%20around%20too%20much%2C%20and%20just%20did%20my%20own%20little%20thing.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20first%20started%20out%20in%20wrestling%2C%20I%20was%20so%20quiet%20and%20timid.%20And%20they%20were%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BYou%20can't%20do%20that%20here