img%20width%3D%5C%225500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Advertisement%20for%20CNN%20presidential%20debate%20in%20Atlanta%2C%20Georgia%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F667b15fb40cf2af6e4f5b33d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThursday's%20presidential%20debate%20is%20the%20first%20ever%20to%20feature%20commercials%2C%20which%20could%20rake%20in%20millions%20not%20only%20for%20CNN%2C%20but%20other%20networks%2C%20too.%3Cp%3EMegan%20Varner%2C%20Reuters%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThursday's%20presidential%20debate%20will%20feature%20commercials%20for%20the%20very%20first%20time%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EStruggling%20with%20ratings%2C%20CNN%20is%20banking%20on%20the%20event%20to%20draw%20in%20viewers%20and%20millions%20in%20revenue%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ERival%20networks%20can%20air%20the%20live%20broadcast%20and%20run%20their%20own%20ads%2C%20setting%20them%20up%20to%20outperform%20CNN%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EFaced%20with%20lagging%20viewership%2C%20CNN%20is%20anticipating%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.in%2Fpolitics%2Fworld%2Fnews%2Fwhat-to-expect-at-biden-and-trumps-first-2024-debate%2Famp_articleshow%2F111239856.cms%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThursday's%20presidential%20debate%3C%2Fa%3E%20will%20rake%20in%20huge%20sums.%20Yet%20other%20networks%20are%20allowed%20to%20air%20the%20live%20broadcast%20of%20the%20showdown%2C%20setting%20them%20up%20to%20outperform%20CNN%20at%20its%20own%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPresident%20Joe%20Biden%20and%20former%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20uncharacteristically%20early%20face-off%20is%20notable%20for%20various%20reasons%2C%20namely%20the%20two%20commercial%20breaks%20that%20will%20splice%20up%20the%2090-minute%20debate.%20Presidential%20debates%20have%20historically%20been%20ad-free%2C%20but%20CNN%20is%20offering%20two%20tiers%20of%20advertising%20this%20year%2C%20with%20the%20most%20robust%20package%20costing%20a%20minimum%20of%20%241.5%20million%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.semafor.com%2Farticle%2F05%2F31%2F2024%2Fcnn-seeks-millions-in-debate-ads%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esources%20told%20Semafor%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20CNN%20is%20hosting%20and%20moderating%20the%20debate%20from%20its%20studios%20in%20Atlanta%2C%20other%20networks%20can%20sell%20their%20own%20advertisements%20during%20their%20simulcasts.%20Given%20that%20some%20of%20those%20networks%2C%20like%20Fox%20News%20and%20MSNBC%2C%20typically%20have%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finsiders-react-to-ex-nyt-mark-thompsons-appointment-cnn-ceo-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elarger%20primetime%20audience%20than%20CNN%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20they%20may%20be%20able%20to%20sell%20advertising%20slots%20for%20more%20money%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ftv%2Fnews%2Fcnn-biden-trump-debate-commercial-breaks-ads-1236020209%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EVariety%20reports%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPer%20CNN's%20rules%2C%20networks%20cannot%20plug%20commercial%20breaks%20with%20commentary%20from%20their%20own%20on-air%20personalities%20and%20must%20keep%20the%20CNN%20logo%20visible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20CNN%20spokesperson%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20network%20is%20making%20the%20debate%20available%20across%20a%20variety%20of%20platforms%20in%20an%20effort%20to%20reach%20as%20many%20people%20as%20possible%2C%20and%20a%20representative%20for%20Fox%20News%20pointed%20to%20the%20network's%20press%20release%20about%20its%20coverage.%20Other%20networks%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20Business%20Insider's%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20cable%20news%20channels%20like%20CNN%20facing%20questions%20about%20their%20futures%2C%20the%20presidential%20election%20serves%20as%20a%20potential%20opportunity%20to%20boost%20viewership.%20As%20Semafor%20notes%2C%20the%20election%20s