l%20arrived%20at%20their%20wedding%20reception%20in%20a%20new%20luxury%20car%20gifted%20by%20Zaheer%2C%20worth%20over%20Rs%202%20crores.%20The%20couple%20shared%20beautiful%20photos%20from%20their%20reception%20at%20Shilpa%20Shetty%E2%80%99s%20Mumbai%20restaurant%2C%20attended%20by%20Bollywood%20stars%20like%20Salman%20Khan%2C%20Rekha%2C%20and%20Anil%20Kapoor.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Akali%20Dal%20Faction%20Talks%20of%20Change%2C%20Wants%20Sukhbir%20Badal%20Out%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Shiromani%20Akali%20Dal%20at%20one%20of%20its%20lowest%20points%20today%2C%20a%20section%20within%20the%20party%20is%20calling%20for%20introspection%20and%20a%20reboot%2C%20preferably%20with%20a%20new%20leader.%20The%20section%20--%20including%20Sikandar%20S%20Maluka%2C%20Surjit%20S%20Rakhra%2C%20Bibi%20Jagir%20Kaur%2C%20Prem%20S%20Chandumajra%20and%20others%20--%20skipped%20a%20crucial%20party%20meeting%20in%20Chandigarh%20to%20hold%20a%20huddle%20of%20their%20own%20in%20Jalandhar.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%26quot%3BToday%20it%20was%20discussed%20seriously%20why%20Akali%20Dal%20has%20become%20so%20weak...%20A%20change%20in%20the%20party%20is%20necessary%20to%20bring%20it%20back%20to%20the%20old%20path%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20senior%20leader%20Prem%20Singh%20Chandumajra%2C%20signalling%20the%20need%20for%20the%20leadership%2C%20to%20take%20responsibility.%20.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%26quot%3BI%20appeal%20to%20party%20chief%20Sukhbir%20Singh%20Badal%20to%20not%20ignore%20the%20sentiments%20of%20the%20workers%2C%20but%20to%20understand%20them.%20The%20party%20will%20take%20a%20decision%20in%20view%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20Election%20results%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20The%20leadership%20of%20the%20Akali%20Dal%20has%20been%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20the%20Badal%20family%20for%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20July%201%2C%20all%20of%20us%20Akali%20leaders%20will%20bow%20down%20in%20Sri%20Akal%20Takht%20Sahib.%20From%20there%20that%20day%2C%20we%20will%20start%20the%20Shiromani%20Akali%20Dal%20Bachao%20Lehar.%20We%20will%20include%20senior%20leaders%20of%20the%20Akali%20Dal%20in%20this%20journey%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20The%20group%20is%20calling%20the%20rejuvenation%20campaign%20the%20%26quot%3BAkali%20Dal%20Bachao%20Abhiyan%26quot%3B.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20Akali%20Dal%2C%20out%20of%20power%20for%20over%20one%20term%2C%20is%20finding%20the%20path%20back%20to%20spotlight%20tough.%20In%202020%2C%20it%20left%20the%20alliance%20with%20the%20BJP%20over%20the%20farm%20law%20issue%20to%20retain%20its%20core%20constituency%20--%20the%20farmers%20of%20the%20state.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnBut%20the%20farmers%20were%20not%20placated%20and%20in%202022%2C%20the%20SAD%20posted%20one%20of%20its%20worst%20performances%20in%20the%20assembly%20election.%20The%20party%20won%20only%20three%20of%20Punjab's%20117%20seats%20and%20the%20Congress%2018.%20AAP%20swept%20the%20election%2C%20winning%2092%20seats.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnIn%20the%20recently%20concluded%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20in%20Punjab%2C%20the%20Akali%20Dal%20could%20hold%20onto%20just%20one%20seat%20--%20Bathinda%20of%20the%20Harsimrat%20Kaur%20Badal%20--%20down%20from%20two%20in%202019.%20The%20Congress%20won%20seven%20of%20the%20state's%2013%20seats%20and%20Arvind%20Kejriwal's%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20three.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnIts%20back%20to%20the%20wall%2C%20the%20party%20is%20now%20contemplating%20on%20some%20serious%20damage%20control%20ahead%20of%20a%20crucial%20by-election%20next%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20July%2010%2C%20by-polls%20are%20due%20in%20the%20Jalandhar%20West%20assembly%20seat.%20By-polls%20for%20four%20more%20seats%20--%20Gidderbaha%2C%20Chabbewal%2C%20Barnala%20and%20Dera%20Baba%20Nanak%20%E2%80%93%20will%20also%20be%20held%20over%20the%20coming%20days.