ndi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fsonakshi-sinha-finally-reacts-to-the-ongoing-trolls-about-her-inter-faith-marriage-with-zaheer-iqbal%2Farticleshow%2F111266709.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F111266709.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ESonakshi%20Sinha's%20wedding%20to%20Zaheer%20Iqbal%20faced%20online%20trolling%2C%20leading%20to%20disabled%20comments.%20She%20shared%20artistic%20wedding%20pictures%20on%20Instagram%20with%20a%20'universal%20religion'%20caption%2C%20followed%20by%20a%20grand%20reception%20attended%20by%20celebrities%20like%20Salman%20Khan%2C%20Kajol%2C%20and%20Vidya%20Balan.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rahul%20Gandhi%20To%20Be%20Leader%20Of%20Opposition%2C%20His%20First%20Constitutional%20Role%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETaking%20the%20fight%20to%20the%20ruling%20BJP-led%20NDA%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20has%20accepted%20a%20decision%20by%20the%20Congress%20Working%20Committee%20and%20will%20take%20up%20the%20mantle%20of%20the%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETuesday's%20announcement%20comes%20hours%20before%20the%20first%20big%20battle%20of%20the%2018th%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20between%20a%20resurgent%20opposition%20and%20a%20diminished%20ruling%20coalition%2C%20over%20the%20post%20of%20Speaker.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDenied%20an%20assurance%20that%20an%20opposition%20member%20would%20be%20given%20the%20post%20of%20Deputy%20Speaker%2C%20as%20is%20the%20tradition%2C%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20decided%20to%20force%20an%20election%20for%20the%20post%20of%20Speaker%20at%20the%20last%20minute%20by%20putting%20up%20K%20Suresh%20as%20its%20candidate%20against%20the%20BJP's%20pick%2C%20Om%20Birla%2C%20who%20was%20the%20Speaker%20in%20the%20previous%20Lok%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Wednesday's%20election%20-%20the%20first%20for%20the%20Speaker's%20post%20in%20decades%20-%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20only%20a%20symbolic%20one%20since%20it%20requires%20a%20simple%20majority%20of%20272%20MPs%20and%20the%20NDA%2C%20which%20has%20293%20on%20its%20own%2C%20has%20also%20got%20the%20support%20of%20the%20YSR%20Congress'%204%20MPs%2C%20it%20is%20about%20the%20opposition%20signalling%20that%20things%20in%20Parliament%20will%20not%20remain%20as%20they%20were%20in%202014%20and%202019.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20move%20to%20make%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20who%20is%20arguably%20the%20Congress'%20most%20popular%20face%2C%20the%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20is%20also%20being%20seen%20as%20a%20step%20in%20that%20direction%20because%20this%20is%20the%20first%20time%20since%202014%20that%20any%20opposition%20party%20has%20managed%20to%20cross%20the%20figure%20of%2054%20(10%25%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha's%20strength)%20needed%20to%20stake%20claim%20to%20the%20post.%20Besides%20getting%20a%20cabinet%20rank%2C%20the%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20post%20will%20enable%20Mr%20Gandhi%20to%20strongly%20take%20up%20the%20issues%20of%20the%20people%20and%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20at%20a%20time%20when%20the%20opposition%20parties%20are%20at%20their%20strongest%20in%20a%20decade.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20are%20expected%20to%20include%20the%20alleged%20paper%20leaks%20in%20various%20examinations%2C%20including%20NEET-UG%2C%20which%20has%20seen%20major%20protests%20in%20several%20parts%20of%20the%20country%20and%20the%20Agnipath%20scheme%20for%20recruitment%20in%20the%20Army%2C%20which%20had%20emerged%20as%20a%20major%20election%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%2C%20Mr%20Gandhi%20will%20be%20part%20of%20key%20panels%20-%20like%20those%20to%20select%20Election%20Commissioners%20and%20the%20CBI%20director%20-%20along%20with%20the%20Prime%20Minister.%20The%20constitutional%20post%20will%20also%20give%20him%20an%20opportunity%20to%20call%20on%20visiting%20heads%20of%20state%20to%20give%20his%20perspective%20on%20national%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20decision%20to%20pick%20Mr%20Gandhi%20for%20the%20post%20was%20announced%20after%20a%20meeting%20of%20floor%20leaders%20of%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20at%20Congress%20President%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge's%20residence%20on%20Tuesday%20night.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCongress%20Parliamentary%20Party%20chairperson%20(Sonia%20Gandhi)%20wrote%20a%20letter%20to%20Pro-Tem%20Speaker%20Bhartruhari%20Mahtab%2C%20informing%20him%20of%20the%20decision%20to%20appoint%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20as%20the%20Leader%20of%20Opposition%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%20Other%20office%20bearers%20will%20be%20decided%20later%2C%26quot%3B%20senior%20party%20leader%20KC%20Venugopal%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%2C%20however%2C%20that%20despite%20the%20timing%20of%20the%20announcement%2C%20the%20Congress'%20allies%20were%20not%20informed%20of%20the%20decision%20at%20the%20INDIA%20meeting.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECWC%20Resolution%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20meeting%20of%20the%20Congress%20Working%20Committee%2C%20the%20party's%20highest%20decision-making%20body%2C%20on%20June%208%20-%20four%20days%20after%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20results%20were%20announced%20-%20a%20resolution%20was%20passed%20stating%20that%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20should%20be%20appointed%20the%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECommending%20his%20role%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20the%20resolution%20also%20said%2C%20%C2%A0%26quot%3BFormer%20Congress%20President%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20has%20to%20be%20singled%20out%20largely%20because%20of%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Yatra%20and%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra%20that%20he%20designed%20and%20led.%20Both%20these%20Yatras%20that%20reflected%20his%20thinking%20and%20personality%20were%20historic%20turning%20points%20in%20our%20nation's%20politics%20and%20instilled%20hope%20and%20confidence%20in%20lakhs%20of%20our%20workers%20and%20crores%20of%20our%20voters.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gandhi%20was%20reportedly%20reluctant%20to%20take%20up%20the%20post%20but%2C%20sources%20said%2C%20he%20gave%20in%20to%20the%20party's%20demands%20and%20was%20also%20prodded%20to%20do%20so%20by%20his%20mother%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20and%20sister%20Priyanka%20Gandhi.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20had%20also%20been%20warned%2C%20in%20jest%2C%20by%20Congress%20President%20Kharge%20that%20disciplinary%20action%20would%20be%20taken%20against%20him%20if%20he%20did%20not%20abide%20by%20the%20Congress%20Working%20Committee's%20decision.%20This%20was%20confirmed%20by%20Mr%20Gandhi%20himself%20when%2C%20while%20the%20party%20was%20announcing%20that%20he%20would%20be%20giving%20up%20the%20Wayanad%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%20and%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20would%20contest%20from%20there%2C%20he%20had%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Ba%20threat%20has%20been%20made%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBig%20Step%20Up%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20will%20be%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20first%20constitutional%20post%20despite%20having%20been%20in%20Parliament%20since%202004.%20Reports%20had%20said%20that%20he%20was%20being%20pushed%20to%20take%20up%20a%20Cabinet%20berth%20between%202004%20and%202014%2C%20when%20the%20UPA%20was%20in%20power%20under%20then%20Prime%20Minister%20Manmohan%20Singh%2C%20but%20he%20had%20declined.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gandhi%20became%20the%20Congress%20president%20in%202017%20and%20resigned%20after%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20taking%20moral%20responsibility%20for%20the%20party's%20poor%20show.%20The%20Congress%20had%20managed%20to%20win%20just%2052%20seats%20-%20up%20from%2044%20in%202014%20-%20while%20the%20BJP%20had%20clinched%20303.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20a%20large%20part%20of%20his%20career%2C%20Mr%20Gandhi%20has%20been%20seen%20as%20a%20not-so-serious%20politician%2C%20especially%20in%20contrast%20to%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20image%20of%20a%2024X7%20worker%20and%20campaigner.%20But%20the%20public%20perception%20of%20the%20Congress%20leader%20began%20to%20change%20after%20the%204%2C000-km%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Yatra%20in%202022-23%20and%20the%206%2C000-km%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra%20earlier%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20reflected%20not%20just%20in%20the%20Congress's%20vastly%20improved%20tally%20of%2099%20seats%20in%20the%20just-concluded%20polls%20but%20also%20in%20Mr%20Gandhi%20winning%20both%20the%20Rae%20Bareli%20and%20Wayanad%20Lok%20Sabha%20constituencies%20with%20margins%20of%20over%203.5%20lakh%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20INDIA%20alliance%2C%20which%20has%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%2C%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20and%20the%20DMK%20as%20the%20other%20major%20constituents%20in%20terms%20of%20strength%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20managed%20to%20win%20232%20seats%20against%20the%20BJP's%20240%20and%20the%20NDA's%20293.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719337020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2F4dlbpp5_rahul-gandhi-ani_625x300_25_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frahul-gandhi-named-as-leader-of-opposition-in-lok-sabha-announces-congress-5968760%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Taking%20the%20fight%20to%20the%20ruling%20BJP-led%20NDA%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20has%20accepted%20a%20decision%20by%20the%20Congress%20Working%20Committee%20and%20will%20take%20up%20the%20mantle%20of%20the%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frahul-gandhi-named-as-leader-of-opposition-in-lok-sabha-announces-congress-5968760%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frahul-gandhi-named-as-leader-of-opposition-in-lok-sabha-announces-congress-5968760%2Fa