0and%20diverse%20narratives.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Indian-Origin%20Woman%20Wrongly%20Jailed%20In%20UK%20During%20Pregnancy%20Rejects%20Apology%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAn%20Indian-origin%20former%20manager%20of%20a%20Post%20Office%20in%20England%20wrongly%20jailed%20while%20pregnant%20has%20rejected%20the%20apology%20of%20an%20engineer%20whose%20evidence%20helped%20convict%20her%20over%20faulty%20accounting%20software.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeema%20Misra%2C%20now%2047%2C%20had%20her%20conviction%20quashed%20in%20April%202021%20as%20the%20Court%20of%20Appeal%20ruled%20that%20she%20had%20been%20wrongly%20imprisoned%20over%2012%20years%20ago%20after%20being%20accused%20of%20stealing%20GBP%2075%2C000%20from%20her%20Post%20Office%20branch%20in%20Surrey%20where%20she%20was%20the%20sub-postmistress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20ongoing%20public%20inquiry%20into%20the%20scandal%2C%20she%20told%20the%20BBC%20that%20the%20apology%20of%20ex-Fujitsu%20engineer%20Gareth%20Jenkins%20was%20%26quot%3Btoo%20little%2C%20too%20late%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNobody%20can%20understand%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20of%20the%20ordeal%20she%20went%20through%20and%20said%20Jenkins%20could%20have%20apologised%20%E2%80%9Cages%20ago%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20reaction%20followed%20a%20written%20witness%20statement%20submitted%20to%20the%20Post%20Office%20Inquiry%20by%20Jenkins%2C%20in%20which%20he%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20did%20not%20know%20that%20Mrs%20Misra%20was%20pregnant%20at%20the%20time%20of%20her%20conviction%20and%20only%20learned%20of%20this%20many%20years%20later.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20makes%20what%20has%20happened%20even%20more%20tragic.%20I%20can%20only%20apologise%2C%20again%2C%20to%20Mrs%20Misra%20and%20her%20family%20for%20what%20happened%20to%20her.%26quot%3B%20The%20former%20engineer%20who%20appeared%20as%20an%20expert%20witness%20in%2015%20sub-postmaster%20cases%20is%20currently%20being%20investigated%20by%20police%20for%20potential%20perjury%20or%20lying%20to%20a%20court.%20In%20one%20of%20his%20earlier%20witness%20statements%20to%20the%20inquiry%2C%20he%20denied%20any%20wrongdoing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20Ms%20Misra%20had%20rejected%20a%20similar%20apology%20from%20former%20Post%20Office%20Managing%20Director%20David%20Smith%20for%20a%20congratulatory%20email%20he%20sent%20after%20Misra's%20conviction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20intended%20to%20be%20a%20congratulatory%20email%20to%20the%20team%2C%20knowing%20that%20they%20had%20worked%20hard%20on%20the%20case%2C%E2%80%9D%20Smith%20said%20in%20his%20written%20evidence%20to%20the%20inquiry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20knowing%20what%20I%20do%20now%2C%20it%20is%20evident%20that%20my%20email%20would%20have%20caused%20Seema%20Misra%20and%20her%20family%20substantial%20distress%20to%20read%20and%20I%20would%20like%20to%20apologise%20for%20that%E2%80%A6%20Even%20if%20this%20had%20been%20a%20correct%20conviction%2C%20I%20would%20absolutely%20never%20think%20that%20it%20was%20%E2%80%98brilliant%20news'%20for%20a%20pregnant%20woman%20to%20go%20to%20prison%20and%20I%20am%20hugely%20apologetic%20that%20my%20email%20can%20be%20read%20as%20such%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20seeing%20this%20email%20in%20the%20light%20of%20what%20I%20know%20now%2C%20I%20understand%20the%20anger%20and%20the%20upset%20that%20it%20will%20have%20caused%20and%20sincerely%20apologise%20for%20that%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20eight%20weeks%20pregnant%20%E2%80%93%20they%20need%20to%20apologise%20to%20my%20youngest%20son.%20It%20was%20terrible.%20I%20haven't%20accepted%20the%20apologies%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Misra%20said%20at%20the%20time%20in%20April.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20had%20my%20conviction%20overturned%2C%20nobody%20came%20at%20that%20time%20to%20apologise.%20And%20now%20they%20just%20suddenly%20realised%20that%20when%20they%20have%20to%20appear%20in%20a%20public%20inquiry%2C%20they%20have%20to%20apologise%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Misra%20was%20sent%20to%20Bronzefield%20prison%20in%20south-east%20England%20and%20served%20four-and-a-half%20months%2C%20later%20giving%20birth%20to%20her%20second%20son%20wearing%20an%20electronic%20tag.%20Smith%20told%20the%20inquiry%20that%20Mr%20Misra%20had%20been%20used%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Btest%20case%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20success%20of%20the%20case%20led%20to%20more%20confidence%20in%20the%20faulty%20Horizon%20IT%20accounting%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHow%20can%20they%20do%20a%20test%20on%20a%20human%20being%3F%20I'm%20a%20living%20creature.%20I%20heard%20that%20my%20case%20has%20been%20used%20as%20a%20test%20case%20before.%20But%20hearing%20it%20again%20and%20again%2C%20it's%20just%20annoying.%20It%20makes%20me%20more%20and%20more%20angry%2C%20to%20be%20honest%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Misra%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UK%20government%2C%20which%20formally%20owns%20Post%20Office%20Ltd%2C%20has%20paid%20out%20millions%20in%20compensation%20to%20hundreds%20of%20sub-postmasters%20-%20many%20of%20them%20of%20Indian%20heritage%20-%20impacted%20by%20the%20faulty%20Horizon%20software.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20year%2C%20British%20Prime%20Minister%20Rishi%20Sunak%20pledged%20action%20in%20the%20historic%20scandal%20that%20wrongly%20accused%20sub-postmasters%20of%20fraud.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20a%20new%20law%20tabled%20in%20Parliament%20introduced%20the%20Post%20Office%20(Horizon%20System)%20Offences%20Bill%2C%20a%20blanket%20exoneration%20to%20quash%20convictions%20brought%20about%20by%20erroneous%20Horizon%20evidence.%20A%20public%20inquiry%20in%20the%20case%2C%20underway%20in%20a%20phased%20manner%2C%20is%20expected%20to%20conclude%20in%20July.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20controversial%20Horizon%20system%2C%20developed%20by%20the%20Japanese%20company%20Fujitsu%2C%20was%20first%20rolled%20out%20in%201999%20to%20some%20post%20offices%20to%20be%20used%20for%20a%20variety%20of%20tasks%2C%20including%20accounting%20and%20stocktaking.%20But%20it%20appeared%20to%20have%20significant%20bugs%2C%20which%20could%20cause%20the%20system%20to%20misreport%2C%20sometimes%20involving%20large%20sums%20as%20was%20the%20case%20in%20the%20case%20of%20these%20sub-postmasters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719336180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fdovl3688_seema-misra_625x300_12_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Findian-origin-woman-wrongly-jailed-in-uk-during-pregnancy-rejects-apology-5969023%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%20Indian-origin%20former%20manager%20of%20a%20Post%20Office%20in%20England%20wrongly%20jailed%20while%20pregnant%20has%20rejected%20the%20apology%20of%20an%20engineer%20whose%20evidence%20helped%20convict%20her%20over%20faulty%20accounting%20software.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Findian-origin-woman-wrongly-jailed-in-uk-during-pregnancy-rejects-apology-5969023%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Findian-origin-woman-wrongly-jailed-in-uk-during-pregnancy-rejects-apology-5969023%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Findian-origin-woman-wrongly-jailed-in-uk-during-pregnancy-rejects-apology-5969023%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India%20at%20cusp%20of%20structural%20growth%20shift%2C%20says%20RBI%20gov%20Shaktikanta%20Das%22%2C%22content%22%3A