%2Farticles%2Fc0xxjn07d6qo%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc0xxjn07d6qo.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc0xxjn07d6qo.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ahead%20Of%20Speaker%20Election%2C%20Parallel%20Meetings%20In%20NDA%2C%20Opposition%20Bloc%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20election%20of%20the%20Speaker%2C%20due%20tomorrow%2C%20might%20be%20slanted%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20government%20the%20way%20the%20numbers%20are%20stacked%20up%2C%20but%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20is%20not%20letting%20grass%20grow%20under%20his%20feet.%20Mr%20Shah%20held%20a%20meeting%20of%20MPs%20and%20party%20leaders%20of%20the%20ruling%20alliance%20this%20evening%20and%20asked%20them%20to%20reach%20parliament%20by%2010.30%20tomorrow%20morning.%20Attendance%20is%20mandatory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20election%20of%20the%20Speaker%20--%20a%20first%20in%20decades%20--%20will%20take%20place%20at%2011%20am.%20Till%20date%2C%20a%20Speaker%20has%20been%20chosen%20by%20consensus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20Opposition%2C%20energised%20by%20their%20numbers%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20has%20refused%20to%20accept%20the%20government's%20brush-off%20on%20the%20issue%20of%20the%20Pro%20Tem%20Speaker%20and%20the%20Deputy%20Speaker's%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Opposition%20initially%20expected%20Mr%20Suresh%20to%20be%20the%20Pro%20Tem%20Speaker%20--%20a%20post%20that%20goes%20to%20the%20seniormost%20member%20of%20the%20House.%20Then%20the%20government%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20they%20are%20not%20considering%20a%20Deputy%20Speaker%20post%2C%20or%20the%20Opposition's%20claim%20to%20it%2C%20for%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%2010%20minutes%20to%20go%20before%20the%20deadline%20today%2C%20the%20Congress%20filed%20papers%20fielding%20Mr%20Suresh%20against%20the%20BJP's%20choice%20--%20Rajasthan%20MP%20Om%20Birla%2C%20who%20was%20the%20Speaker%20in%20the%2017th%20Lok%20Sabha%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20numbers%2C%20as%20they%20stand%20now%2C%20does%20not%20favour%20the%20Opposition.%20The%20Speaker%20is%20elected%20by%20a%20simple%20majority%20of%20MPs%20present%20and%20voting.%20The%20NDA%20can%20expect%20293%20votes%20to%20the%20Opposition%20bloc's%20232.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20that%20end%2C%20Mr%20Shah%20held%20a%20meeting%20which%20was%20attended%20by%20Bihar%20allies%20Chirag%20Paswan%2C%20JItam%20Ram%20Manjhi%20and%20a%20few%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20Opposition%20parties%2C%20too%2C%20have%20issued%20whips%20to%20ensure%20there%20is%20no%20absenteeism.%20A%20meeting%20will%20be%20held%20at%20the%20house%20of%20Congress%20chief%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20this%20evening%2C%20which%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%2C%20initially%20miffed%20about%20not%20being%20consulted%20for%20the%20big%20step%2C%20will%20attend.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnion%20minister%20Kiren%20Rijiju%2C%20who%20handles%20the%20Parliamentary%20Affairs%20portfolio%2C%20issued%20a%20last%20appeal%20for%20a%20consensus%20candidate.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20the%20last%20two%20days%2C%20we%20have%20been%20in%20contact%20with%20main%20Opposition%20parties%2C%20talked%20to%20their%20floor%20leaders%20regarding%20the%20post%20of%20Speaker.%20Since%20the%20Independence%2C%20there%20has%20not%20been%20an%20election%20for%20Speaker%20post.%20We%20want%20speaker%20to%20be%20elected%20unopposed%20and%20through%20consensus%2C%26quot%3Bhe%20told%20reporters.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn.%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20Congress%20and%20its%20leaders%20had%20joined%20the%20NDA%20meeting%2C%20he%20said%2C%20but%20wanted%20an%20immediate%20decision%20on%20the%20deputy%20Speaker.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20appealed%20to%20them%20to%20support%20the%20Speaker%20candidate%20but%20they%20demanded%20Deputy%20Speaker%20post.%20We%20said%20it%20is%20not%20right%20to%20conduct%20election%20for%20both%20Speaker%20and%20Deputy%20Speaker%20posts%20together.%20We%20want%20Speaker%20with%20consensus%20and%20then%20we%20will%20talk%20about%20Deputy%20Speaker%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress's%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20has%20alleged%20that%20though%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20talks%20of%20constructive%20support%20from%20the%20Opposition%2C%20he%20%26quot%3Bdoes%20not%20want%20any%20constructive%20cooperation%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20example%2C%20he%20said%20Union%20minister%20Rajnath%20Singh%20%E2%80%93%20tasked%20to%20build%20consensus%20on%20the%20Speaker%20post%20%E2%80%93%20did%20not%20call%20Congress%20chief%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%2C%20which%20is%20%26quot%3Ban%20insult%20to%20our%20leader%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719326400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fo6f8hu6s_amit-shah-rahul-gandhi_625x300_25_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fahead-of-speaker-election-parallel-meeting-in-nda-opposition-blocs-5967686%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20election%20of%20the%20Speaker%2C%20due%20tomorrow%2C%20might%20be%20slanted%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20government%20the%20way%20the%20numbers%20are%20stacked%20up%2C%20but%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20is%20not%20letting%20grass%20grow%20under%20his%20feet.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fahead-of-speaker-election-parallel-meeting-in-nda-opposition-blocs-5967686%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fahead-of-speaker-election-parallel-meeting-in-nda-opposition-blocs-5967686%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fahead-of-speaker-election-parallel-meeting-in-nda-opposition-blocs-5967686%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22No%20Leakage%20In%20Ram%20Temple%2C%20Rainwater%20Trickled%20From%20Pipes%2C%20Says%20Trust%20Chief%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ERam%20Temple%20Construction%20Committee%20Chairman%20Nripendra%20Mishra%20on%20Tuesday%20rejected%20the%20allegations%20of%20the%20temple's%20chief%20priest%20regarding%20the%20seepage%20of%20rainwater%20draining%20out%20of%20water%20from%20the%20sanctum%20sanctorum.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20was%20no%20water%20leakage%20but%20the%20rainwater%20came%20down%20from%20the%20pipes%20fixed%20to%20install%20electric%20wires%2C%26quot%3B%20Mishra%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20myself%20have%20inspected%20the%20building%20of%20the%20temple.%20The%20second%20floor%20is%20under%20construction.%20When%20the%20roof%20of%20the%20second%20floor%20will%20be%20finally%20constructed%2C%20then%20the%20rainwater%20will%20stop%20entering%20the%20temple%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Mishra%20told%20reporters%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlleging%20negligence%20in%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20temple%2C%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20temple%20chief%20priest%20Acharya%20Satyendra%20Das%20had%20on%20Monday%20alleged%20that%20there%20was%20no%20arrangement%20for%20the%20draining%20out%20of%20rainwater%20from%20the%20temple%20premises%20after%20the%20showers%20on%20Saturday%20midnight%20and%20urged%20the%20temple%20authorities%20to%20take%20necessary%20corrective%20measures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Das%20had%20asked%20the%20temple%20authorities%20to%20take%20cognisance%20of%20the%20incident%20and%20make%20necessary%20arrangements%20to%20stop%20leakage%20and%20ensure%20outflow%20of%20water%20from%20the%20temple.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20had%20claimed%20that%20there%20was%20heavy%20leakage%20from%20the%20roof%20of%20the%20temple's%20sanctum%20sanctorum%20in%20the%20first%20heavy%20showers%20that%20occurred%20at%20midnight%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERainwater%20was%20leaking%20from%20the%20roof%20directly%20above%20the%20place%20where%20the%20priest%20sits%20in%20front%20of%20Ram%20Lalla's%20idol%20and%20where%20people%20come%20for%20VIP%20'darshan'%2C%20he%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20very%20surprising%20that%20engineers%20from%20all%20over%20the%20country%20are%20building%20the%20Ram%20temple.%20The%20temple%20was%20inaugurated%20on%20January%2022.%20But%2C%20no%20one%20knew%20that%20if%20it%20rains%2C%20the%20roof%20will%20leak.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20surprising%20that%20the%20roof%20of%20a%20world%20famous%20temple%20is%20leaking.%20Why%20did%20this%20happen%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuch%20an%20incident%20is%20happening%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20such%20big%20engineers%2C%20which%20is%20very%20wrong%2C%20he%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Mishra%20said%20measures%20have%20been%20taken%20to%20protect%20the%20devotees%20from%20water%20and%20sunlight%20by%20making%20temporary%20construction%20on%20the%20roof.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbout%20the%20progress%20of%20temple%20construction%2C%20Mr%20Mishra%20said%20work%20on%20the%20first%20floor%20was%20on%20and%20will%20be%20finished%20by%20July%20this%20year.%20He%20expressed%20the%20hope%20that%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20temple%20would%20be%20completed%20by%20December.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719326280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fkr8tmlig_ram-temple-_625x300_24_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fno-leakage-in-ram-temple-rainwater-trickled-from-pipes-says-trust-chief-nripendra-mishra-5967906%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ram%20Temple%20Construction%20Committee%20Chairman%20Nripendra%20Mishra%20on%20Tuesday%20rejected%20the%20allegations%20of%20the%20temple's%20chief%20priest%20regarding%20the%20seepage%20of%20rainwater%20draining%20out%20of%20water%20from%20the%20sanctum%20sanctorum.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22htt