ocketlane-raises-24-million-in-series-b-funding-round-124062501070_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Indians%20Spend%20Almost%20Twice%20On%20Weddings%20Than%20On%20Education%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndians%20spend%20nearly%20double%20on%20weddings%20compared%20to%20what%20they%20spend%20on%20education%2C%20a%20new%20report%20has%20revealed.%20The%20Indian%20wedding%20market%20is%20valued%20at%20an%20astounding%20%24130%20billion%20(approximately%20%E2%82%B910.7%20lakh%20crore)%2C%20twice%20the%20size%20of%20the%20US%20wedding%20market%2C%20according%20to%20a%20recent%20report%20by%20Jefferies%2C%20an%20investment%20banking%20and%20capital%20market%20firm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20comprehensive%20study%20was%20based%20on%20various%20available%20data%20and%20visits%20to%20key%20industry%20hubs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWedding%20vs%20Education%20expenses%20in%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20average%20cost%20of%20an%20Indian%20wedding%20is%20around%20%2415%2C000%20(approximately%20%E2%82%B912.5%20lakh)%2C%20the%20report%20said.%20This%20is%20nearly%20double%20what%20an%20average%20Indian%20couple%20spends%20on%20education%20from%20pre-primary%20to%20graduation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEconomic%20impact%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20wedding%20market%20is%20twice%20the%20size%20of%20the%20US%20market%20but%20smaller%20than%20China's.%20On%20average%2C%20Indians%20spend%20five%20times%20the%20country's%20per%20capita%20GDP%20of%20%242%2C900%20(over%20%E2%82%B92.4%20lakh)%20on%20weddings%20and%20more%20than%20three%20times%20the%20average%20annual%20household%20income%20of%20around%20%E2%82%B94%20lakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELuxury%20weddings%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELuxury%20weddings%2C%20which%20cost%20between%20%E2%82%B920%20lakh%20and%20%E2%82%B930%20lakh%2C%20represent%20a%20significant%20portion%20of%20the%20market%2C%20with%20the%20upper%20end%20being%20much%20more%20extravagant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20budgets%20typically%20cover%20expenses%20for%20hosting%20five%20to%20six%20functions%2Fevents%2C%20luxurious%20accommodations%20at%20top-tier%20hotels%2C%20lavish%20catering%2C%20decor%2C%20and%20entertainment%2C%20though%20expenses%20related%20to%20jewellery%2C%20wedding%20attire%2C%20and%20airfare%20are%20not%20included.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGrowth%20of%20sectors%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20wedding%20industry%20is%20made%20up%20of%20many%20small%20businesses%20and%20individual%20service%20providers.%20This%20is%20because%20different%20regions%20have%20unique%20wedding%20traditions%2C%20allowing%20local%20businesses%20to%20cater%20to%20specific%20needs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndian%20weddings%20boost%20several%20industries%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJewellery%20-%20Over%20half%20of%20jewellery%20sales%20come%20from%20bridal%20jewellery.%20Apparel%3A%20More%20than%2010%25%20of%20clothing%20spending%20is%20for%20weddings.%20Catering%20and%20events%3A%20Catering%20makes%20up%2020%25%20of%20wedding%20costs%2C%20while%20events%20make%20up%2015%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20encouraged%20Indians%20to%20%26quot%3Bwed%20in%20India%26quot%3B%20instead%20of%20going%20abroad%20for%20destination%20weddings.%20This%20aims%20to%20support%20the%20local%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719325140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-01%2Fellf7tio_indian-wedding-generic_625x300_24_January_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findians-spending-almost-twice-on-weddings-than-on-education-report-5966043%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Indians%20spend%20nearly%20double%20on%20weddings%20compared%20to%20what%20they%20spend%20on%20education%2C%20a%20new%20report%20has%20revealed.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findians-spending-almost-twice-on-weddings-than-on-education-report-5966043%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findians-spending-almost-twice-on-weddings-than-on-education-report-5966043%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findians-spending-almost-twice-on-weddings-than-on-education-report-5966043%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22UP%20Engineer-Rapper-YouTuber%20Turns%20Robber%20Over%20%26quot%3BFinancial%20Crisis%26quot%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAn%20engineer%2C%20a%20rapper%2C%20YouTuber%20and%20now%20a%20robber%20too%20-%20this%20is%20how%20a%20man%20from%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20can%20be%20described%20who%20mugged%20an%20Ola%20driver%20as%20he%20was%20going%20through%20a%20%26quot%3Bfinancial%20crisis%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20man%20was%20arrested%20from%20Ayodhya%20by%20the%20Delhi%20Police%20yesterday%20for%20shooting%20at%20and%20robbing%20the%20driver%2C%20Kulbhushan%20Sharma%2C%20of%20his%20mobile%20and%20cash%20in%20the%20national%20capital's%20Amar%20Colony%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20accused%20told%20police%20he%20became%20a%20rapper%20after%20he%20failed%20to%20land%20a%20job%20even%20after%20studying%20computer%20science%20engineering.%20Even%20his%20career%20as%20a%20rapper%20failed%20to%20take%20off%20and%20that%20is%20why%2C%20he%20told%20the%20police%2C%20he%20committed%20the%20robbery.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20got%20a%20call%20about%20the%20incident%20on%20June%2023%20at%201.30%20am.%20When%20they%20reached%20the%20spot%2C%20they%20found%20the%20Ola%20car%2C%20the%20driver%2C%20however%2C%20had%20been%20shifted%20to%20a%20hospital%20by%20then.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20man%2C%20who%20boarded%20the%20cab%20from%20Dwarka%20Mod%2C%20had%20booked%20a%20ride%20till%20Kashmiri%20Gate%20bus%20stand%2C%20the%20driver%20told%20the%20police%2C%20adding%20on%20the%20way%2C%20he%20pointed%20a%20pistol%20and%20looted%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20car's%20fuel%20got%20low%2C%20he%20stopped%20at%20the%20petrol%20pump%20in%20Srinivas%20Puri%20area.%20He%20then%20snatched%20the%20driver's%20mobile%20phone%20and%20money.%20A%20frightened%20Mr%20Sharma%20got%20out%20of%20the%20car%20somehow%20and%20tried%20to%20flee%20the%20scene%20but%20the%20accused%20shot%20at%20him%2C%20injuring%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20soon%20after%20registered%20a%20case%20of%20robbery%20and%20attempt%20to%20murder%20and%20started%20investigating%20the%20matter.%20They%20scanned%20all%20the%20CCTV%20cameras%20on%20the%20route%20taken%20by%20the%20car.%20After%20going%20through%20the%20booking%20details%20in%20the%20Ola%20app%2C%20the%20accused%20was%20identified%20as%20Aryan%20Rajvansh%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20Ayodhya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20arrested%20from%20his%20house%20in%20Ayodhya%20police%20arrested%20him.%20Aryan%20Rajvansh%20told%20them%20that%20he%20had%20come%20to%20Delhi%20to%20collect%20some%20of%20his%20belongings%20from%20a%20friend's%20room.%20Mr%20Rajvansh%2C%20who%20did%20his%20Btech%20in%20Computer%20Science%20from%20Sri%20Ishwar%20College%20of%20Engineering%20in%20Coimbatore%2C%20said%20that%20he%20planned%20to%20rob%20the%20driver%20as%20he%20was%20going%20through%20a%20financial%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20told%20the%20police%20that%20he%20was%20carrying%20the%20pistol%20with%20him%20when%20he%20travelled%20from%20Ayodhya%20to%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719325080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2F7j4g5e9g_aryan-rajvansh_625x300_25_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fup-man-robs-ola-driver-after-careers-as-engineer-rapper-fail-to-take-off-5967941%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%20engineer%2C%20a%20rapper%2C%20YouTuber%20and%20now%20a%20robber%20too%20-%20this%20is%20how%20a%20man%20from%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20can%20be%20described%20who%20mugged%20an%20Ola%20driver%20