Pradesh%2C%20where%20its%20tally%20was%20reduced%20to%2033%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20from%2062%20in%202019.%20The%20results%20came%20as%20a%20shock%20to%20the%20BJP%2C%20which%20also%20became%20the%20second-largest%20party%20in%20the%20state%20in%20terms%20of%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%2C%20behind%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20Mr%20Kishan's%20swearing-in%2C%20AIMIM%20Chief%20Asaduddin%20Owaisi%20sparked%20controversy%20by%20expressing%20solidarity%20with%20the%20people%20of%20Palestine%20after%20taking%20oath%20as%20the%20Hyderabad%20MP%20for%20the%20fifth%20time.%20Members%20of%20the%20treasury%20benches%20objected%20to%20this%20and%20were%20assured%20by%20Radha%20Mohan%20Singh%2C%20who%20was%20chairing%20the%20proceedings%20at%20the%20time%2C%20that%20any%20statements%20beyond%20the%20formal%20oath%20would%20not%20be%20recorded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20reporters%20later%2C%20Mr%20Owaisi%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BOther%20members%20are%20also%20saying%20different%20things.%20I%20said%20'Jai%20Bheem%2C%20Jai%20Meem%2C%20Jai%20Telangana%2C%20Jai%20Palestine'.%20How%20is%20it%20wrong%3F%20Tell%20me%20the%20provision%20of%20the%C2%A0%20Constitution.%20You%20should%20also%20listen%20to%20what%20others%20said.%20I%20said%20what%20I%20had%20to.%20Read%20what%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20had%20said%20about%20Palestine.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719324780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2F03he1up8_ravi-kishan_625x300_25_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fafter-ravi-kishans-oath-as-mp-for-2nd-time-a-har-har-mahadev-chant-5968028%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Being%20sworn%20in%20as%20a%20Lok%20Sabha%20MP%20for%20the%20second%20time%2C%20BJP%20leader%20Ravi%20Kishan%20ended%20his%20oath%20by%20invoking%20a%20yogi%2C%20chanting%20a%20Hindu%20religious%20mantra%20and%20shouting%20a%20slogan%20hailing%20the%20Bhojpuri%20language%20and%20the%20people%20who%20speak%20it.%22%2C%2