rent%20and%20must%20plan%20accordingly.%20%E2%80%9CDo%20not%20copy%20anyone.%20Play%20on%20your%20strengths%20and%20weaknesses%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHere%20are%20a%20few%20tips%20to%20keep%20your%20mind%20calm%3A%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EStudy%20smarter%20and%20study%20harder%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESolve%20previous%20years%E2%80%99%20question%20(PYQ)%20papers%20and%20understand%20the%20topics%20UPSC%20has%20loved%20all%20these%20years.%20%E2%80%9CBy%20PYQs%2C%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20mean%20just%20the%20questions%20but%20also%20the%20options.%20Observe%20why%20a%20question%20has%20been%20asked%2C%20rather%20than%20just%20seeing%20what%20has%20been%20asked%2C%20to%20understand%20the%20psyche%20of%20the%20question%20paper%20setter%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%222%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EDon%E2%80%99t%20stop%2C%20but%20learn%20when%20to%20let%20go%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaruni%20quit%20her%20MBBS%20after%20two%20years%20due%20to%20a%20health%20problem.%20%E2%80%9CNever%20giving%20up%20is%20a%20good%20attitude%20that%20we%20all%20have%20been%20taught%20since%20we%20were%20kids.%20I%20made%20a%20similar%20mistake%20by%20not%20leaving%20my%20MBBS%20course%20early%20because%20I%20always%20felt%20that%20if%20I%20quit%2C%20it%20would%20be%20my%20failure.%20I%20realised%20later%20that%20there%20were%20equally%20good%20things%20in%20life%20waiting%20for%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Taruni.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20urges%20aspirants%20to%20make%20their%20own%20decisions%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20quitting%20or%20giving%20the%20exam%20another%20shot.%20%E2%80%9CListen%20to%20your%20conscience%20without%20paying%20any%20heed%20to%20the%20outside%20world%20and%20their%20set%20formats%20of%20success%20and%20failure%2C%20and%20you%20will%20get%20the%20correct%20answer.%20Move%20ahead%20with%20minimal%20regrets%20because%20zero%20regrets%20don%E2%80%99t%20exist%20for%20mere%20humans%20like%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%223%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EBe%20mindful%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDo%20something%20that%20connects%20you%20to%20something%20bigger%20than%20your%20goal.%20%E2%80%9CMeditate%2C%20take%20a%20walk%20in%20nature%2C%20sit%20under%20the%20moon%2C%20listen%20to%20birds%20and%20so%20on.%20This%20reminds%20you%20that%20your%20goals%20are%20not%20the%20ultimate%20objective%20but%20merely%20a%20part%20of%20the%20bigger%20plan.%20It%20keeps%20you%20grounded.%20Any%20type%20of%20meditation%20or%20journaling%20keeps%20you%20sane%20during%20this%20hard%20phase%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%224%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EWrite%20it%20on%20paper!%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaruni%20has%20always%20jotted%20down%20her%20dreams%2C%20plans%20and%20more.%20She%20urges%20aspirants%20to%20write%20their%20feelings%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20get%20clarity%20when%20you%20see%20things%20organised%20visually%20in%20front%20of%20you.%20Look%20at%20your%20triggers%20with%20an%20open%20mind%20and%20eliminate%20the%20ones%20you%20can%2C%20mark%20the%20ones%20you%20need%20to%20work%20on.%20Let%20go%20of%20the%20ones%20that%20are%20beyond%20your%20control.%20Belief%20is%20a%20very%20important%20virtue%20that%20will%20help%20you%20the%20most%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F347611%2Fupsc-cse-2023-final-list-toppers-ias-officer-jitin-yadav-viral-tweet-on-failure-aspirants-inspiration%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eduring%20your%20preparation%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIf%20you%20wish%20to%20ask%20her%20any%20questions%2C%20you%20can%20drop%20Taruni%20a%20message%20on%20Instagram%20at%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20h