2%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Specialist%20search%20dogs%20have%20been%20drafted%20in%20from%20the%20Spanish%20capital%20Madrid%20to%20help%20in%20the%20hunt%20for%20missing%20British%20teenager%20Jay%20Slater.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4874%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fjay-slater-specialist-search-dogs-brought-in-to-hunt-for-missing-teenager-13158623%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fjay-slater-specialist-search-dogs-brought-in-to-hunt-for-missing-teenager-13158623%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fjay-slater-specialist-search-dogs-brought-in-to-hunt-for-missing-teenager-13158623%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Antarctic%20Study%20Reveals%20%26quot%3BTipping%20Point%26quot%3B%20For%20Runaway%20Melting%20Of%20Ice%20Sheets%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EScientists%20have%20discovered%20a%20new%20tipping%20point%20toward%20%26quot%3Brunaway%20melting%26quot%3B%20of%20Antarctic%20ice%20sheets%2C%20caused%20by%20warm%20ocean%20water%20intruding%20between%20the%20ice%20and%20the%20land%20it%20sits%20on%2C%20according%20to%20a%20study%20published%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20this%20type%20of%20melting%20has%20been%20previously%20studied%2C%20models%20used%20by%20the%20United%20Nations%20Intergovernmental%20Panel%20on%20Climate%20Change%20(IPCC)%20to%20project%20the%20impact%20of%20global%20warming%20on%20the%20Antarctic%20have%20yet%20to%20factor%20in%20this%20phenomenon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20have%20also%20systematically%20underestimated%20ice%20loss%20seen%20thus%20far%2C%20said%20the%20study%2C%20published%20in%20the%20journal%20Nature%20Geoscience.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20ocean%20temperatures%20rise%20due%20to%20human-caused%20global%20warming%2C%20Antarctic%20ice%20sheets%20are%20melting%2C%20threatening%20a%20rise%20in%20global%20sea%20levels%20and%20putting%20coastal%20communities%20at%20risk.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIncreases%20in%20ocean%20temperature%20can%20lead%20to%20a%20tipping%20point%20being%20passed%2C%20beyond%20which%20ocean%20water%20intrudes%20in%20an%20unbounded%20manner%20beneath%20the%20ice%20sheet%2C%20via%20a%20process%20of%20runaway%20melting%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20study%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAntarctic%20ice%20sheets%20sit%20atop%20the%20bedrock%20and%20extend%20beyond%20the%20coast%20to%20float%20on%20the%20sea.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrevious%20studies%20have%20shown%20that%20warm%20seawater%20is%20seeping%20into%20the%20%26quot%3Bgrounding%20zone%26quot%3B%20--%20where%20land%20and%20ice%20meet%20--%20and%20further%20inland%20from%20under%20the%20floating%20ice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20water%20warms%2C%20even%20by%20a%20fraction%2C%20the%20intrusion%20accelerates%20from%20short%20distances%20of%20100%20metres%20(330%20feet)%20to%20tens%20of%20kilometres%20(miles)%2C%20melting%20ice%20along%20the%20way%20by%20heating%20it%20from%20below%2C%20explained%20the%20study's%20lead%20author%20Alexander%20Bradley.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEvery%2010th%20of%20a%20degree%20(of%20warming)%20makes%20these%20kind%20of%20processes%20closer%2C%20these%20tipping%20points%20closer%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Bradley%2C%20a%20researcher%20with%20the%20British%20Antarctic%20Survey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20risk%20to%20sea-level%20rise%20comes%20when%20the%20accelerated%20melting%20outpaces%20the%20formation%20of%20new%20ice%20on%20the%20continent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20areas%20of%20Antarctica%20are%20more%20vulnerable%20to%20this%20process%20than%20others%20due%20to%20the%20shape%20of%20the%20land%20mass%2C%20which%20has%20valleys%20and%20cavities%20where%20sea%20water%20can%20pool%20beneath%20the%20ice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Pine%20Island%20glacier%2C%20currently%20Antarctica's%20largest%20contributor%20to%20sea-level%20rise%2C%20is%20at%20high%20risk%20of%20melting%20due%20to%20the%20slope%20of%20the%20land%20that%20allows%20in%20more%20seawater%2C%20the%20study%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EScientific%20models%20need%20to%20be%20updated%20to%20take%20into%20account%20the%20element%20of%20melt%20to%20better%20predict%20the%20risk%20of%20sea-level%20rise%20in%20the%20future%20and%20prepare%20for%20it%2C%20Bradley%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20it%20really%20just%20stresses%20the%20need%20for%20urgent%20climate%20action%20in%20order%20to%20prevent%20these%20tipping%20points%20from%20being%20passed%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719319800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fh4p22gho_antarctic-ice_625x300_25_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fantarctic-study-reveals-tipping-point-for-runaway-melting-of-ice-sheets-5967122%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Scientists%20have%20discovered%20a%20new%20tipping%20point%20toward%20%26quot%3Brunaway%20melting%26quot%3B%20of%20Antarctic%20ice%20sheets%2C%20caused%20by%20warm%20ocean%20water%20intruding%20between%20the%20ice%20and%20the%20land%20it%20sits%20on%2C%20according%20to%20a%20study%20published%20on%20Tuesday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fantarctic-study-reveals-tipping-point-for-runaway-melting-of-ice-sheets-5967122%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fantarctic-study-reveals-tipping-point-for-runaway-melting-of-ice-sheets-5967122%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fantarctic-study-reveals-tipping-point-for-runaway-melting-of-ice-sheets-5967122%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Protesters%20'shot%20dead'%20in%20Kenya%20as%20parliament%20set%20on%20fire%20after