0Karnataka%2C%20Ulikkal%20village%20in%20the%20Kannur%20district%20was%20a%20lush%20landscape%20that%20was%20once%20predominantly%20a%20rubber-growing%20area.%20Among%20millions%20of%20rubber%20farmers%2C%20Biju%20Narayanan%E2%80%99s%20family%20who%20cultivated%20rubber%20on%20one-third%20of%20the%20farmland%2C%20also%20lost%20their%20major%20income%20source%20with%20plummeting%20profitability.%20It%20became%20costlier%20to%20produce%20rubber%20than%20to%20sell%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20average%20cost%20of%20production%20was%20around%20Rs%20160%20per%20kg%20and%20the%20selling%20price%20was%20Rs%20110%20per%20kg.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20rates%20in%20rubber%20were%20dwindling%20as%20farmers%20could%20fetch%20only%20Rs%20100%20per%20kg%20from%20rubber.%20A%20labourer%20could%20earn%20more%20wages%20daily.%20It%20was%20not%20sufficient%20for%20farmers%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiju%20reconsidered%20the%20agricultural%20practices%20and%20made%20the%20bold%20decision%20to%20replace%20seven%20acres%20of%20his%20family%E2%80%99s%20rubber%20trees%20with%20a%20variety%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F295835%2Fcoconut-farmer-senior-citizen-grows-mangosteen-from-malaysia-exports-to-gulf-countries%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexotic%20fruits%3C%2Fa%3E%20like%20rambutan%2C%20mangosteen%2C%20pepper%2C%20areca%20nut%2C%20coconut%2C%20cashew%2C%20and%20other%20crops.%20%E2%80%9CI%20axed%20most%20of%20the%20rubber%20trees%20to%20try%20new%20plantations.%20People%20called%20me%20a%20madman%2C%E2%80%9D%20laughs%20the%20progressive%20farmer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FBiju-1_11zon-1719236290.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Biju%20opted%20for%20high-density%20plantations%20and%20multi-crops%20to%20maximise%20returns%20from%20land.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FBiju-1_11zon-1719236290.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FBiju-1_11zon-1719236290-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FBiju-1_11zon-1719236290-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FBiju-1_11zon-1719236290-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FBiju-1_11zon-1719236290-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-354131%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EBiju%20opted%20for%20high-density%20plantations%20and%20multi-crops%20to%20maximise%20returns%20from%20land.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20decision%2C%20once%20criticised%20and%20deemed%20as%20madness%20by%20many%2C%20including%20his%20own%20family%2C%20has%20since%20blossomed%20into%20a%20lucrative%20agribusiness%20model.%20%E2%80%9CI%20knew%20I%20must%20prove%20my%20decision%20correct%20because%20my%20family%2C%20neighbours%2C%20and%20friends%20thought%20it%20was%20a%20crazy%20decision.%20I%20took%20it%20as%20a%20challenge%20and%20turned%20agriculture%20into%20agri-business%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20Biju%20earns%20Rs%209%20to%2015%20lakh%20per%20acre%20from%20rambutan%20farming%20alone.%20We%20sat%20down%20with%20him%20to%20understand%20how%20he%20rewrote%20the%20traditional%20farming%20script.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMaximising%20yield%20with%20multi-crops%20on%20the%20same%20land%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiju%20is%20a%20mechanical%20engineer%20by%20profession.%20Educated%20at%20Dakshina%20Kannada%E2%80%99s%20KVG%20College%20of%20Engineering%2C%20he%20initially%20juggled%20his%20studies%20with%20managing%20the%