instagram.com%2Fbepolite_city%2F%3Fhl%3Den%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E4.%20Solar%20power%20for%20making%20%3Cem%3Erotis%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20article%20posted%20by%20the%20%3Cem%3EMinistry%20of%20New%20and%20Renewable%20Energy%3C%2Fem%3E%20narrated%20the%20story%20of%20two%20women%2C%20Joshi%20and%20Rosy%2C%20who%20used%20solar%20power%20to%20their%20advantage%20to%20create%20thriving%20home%20businesses%20%E2%80%94%20displaying%20an%20appetite%20for%20innovation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Joshi%E2%80%99s%20case%2C%20it%20was%20the%20untimely%20death%20of%20her%20husband%20that%20led%20her%20to%20start%20a%20catering%20business.%20But%20while%20she%20enjoyed%20cooking%2C%20making%20%3Cem%3Erotis%20%3C%2Fem%3E(Indian%20flatbreads)%20was%20proving%20to%20be%20a%20time-consuming%20ordeal%20as%20milling%20the%20flour%20would%20take%20her%20hours%3B%20sometimes%20an%20entire%20day.%20Frequent%20power%20cuts%20were%20of%20no%20help.%20But%20hope%20came%20in%20the%20form%20of%20a%20solar-powered%20rob-rolling%20machine%20and%20a%20flour-milling%20machine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20same%20success%20was%20tasted%20by%20Rosy%20Louis%20Dabale%20from%20the%20village%20of%20Agsalkatta%20in%20North%20Karnataka.%20Rosy%20is%20a%20health%20worker%20in%20the%20village%2C%20according%20to%20the%20article%2C%20and%20she%20now%20manages%20the%20flour%20mill%20on%20the%20premises.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E5.%20%C2%A0Solar%20power%20for%20tailoring%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsolar-power-1718978521.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tailoring%20is%20one%20of%20the%20home-run%20businesses%20that%20is%20starting%20to%20see%20solar%20power%20be