enu%20curation%2C%20outfit%20design%20and%20styling%2C%20and%20creative%20direction.%20They%20curate%20%E2%80%9Cfood%2C%20clothing%2C%20and%20art%E2%80%9D%20with%20a%20common%20thread%20of%20local%20essence%2C%20says%20the%20entrepreneur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWeaving%20a%20story%20around%20food%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20common%20thread%20throughout%20Akash%E2%80%99s%20life%20has%20been%20his%20need%20to%20share%20food%20stories.%20In%202021%2C%20he%20undertook%20a%20100-day%20cooking%20project%20to%20shed%20light%20on%20forgotten%20vegetables.%20His%20vision%20for%20participating%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F305138%2Fmasterchef-india-contestant-whips-up-gluten-free-desserts-in-her-house-of-millets%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMasterChef%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%20Tamil%20was%20also%20driven%20by%20a%20desire%20to%20share%20the%20story%20of%20South%20Indian%20food.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSouth%20Indian%20cooking%20has%20a%20lot%20to%20offer.%20It%E2%80%99s%20not%20explored%20as%20much%20as%20it%20should%20be.%20When%20Indian%20food%20is%20spoken%20about%20internationally%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20usually%20identified%20with%20breads%20like%20%3Cem%3Enaan%3C%2Fem%3E.%20I%20want%20to%20make%20equivalents%20from%20the%20Southern%20part%20of%20the%20country%20shine%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Akash.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%E2%80%99s%20precisely%20what%20he%20did%20during%20the%20show.%20His%20finale%20dish%2C%20which%20included%20a%20main%20course%20and%20dessert%2C%20celebrated%20and%20elevated%20the%20humble%20%3Cem%3Epongal%3C%2Fem%3E%20(made%20with%20rice%20and%20green%20gram)%2C%20both%20savoury%20and%20sweet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC8KYOJ6SyA6%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noo