n%20the%20affected%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsocial-town-2-1718888491.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Neenu%20has%20helped%20over%205000%20stakeholders%20including%20changemakers%2C%20NGOs%20and%20social%20entrepreneurs.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsocial-town-2-1718888491.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsocial-town-2-1718888491-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsocial-town-2-1718888491-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsocial-town-2-1718888491-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsocial-town-2-1718888491-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-353673%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ENeenu%20has%20helped%20over%205000%20stakeholders%20including%20changemakers%2C%20NGOs%20and%20social%20entrepreneurs.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20experience%20made%20me%20realise%20the%20power%20of%20collective%20action.%20Back%20in%202013%2C%20I%20had%20already%20wanted%20to%20create%20a%20platform%20for%20people%20like%20me%20who%20were%20passionate%20about%20social%20change.%20Although%20I%20was%20working%20with%20the%20Art%20of%20Living%20Foundation%2C%20I%20had%20limited%20connections%20with%20other%20social%20impact%20organisations%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNo%20one%20in%20my%20family%20had%20been%20involved%20in%20social%20work%2C%20so%20this%20was%20my%20first%20introduction%20to%20such%20projects%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%202019%20floods%20also%2C%20Neenu%20actively%20participated%20in%20the%20rehabilitation%20of%20people%20affected%20by%20the%20disaster%2C%20particularly%20focusing%20on%20tribal%20settlements%20in%20Attapadi%2C%20Nilambur%2C%20and%20Wayanad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20the%20motivation%20that%20came%20from%20helping%20people%20in%20need%20kept%20me%20going%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202020%2C%20when%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20hit%2C%20Neenu%20realised%20that%20it%20was%20important%20for%20her%20to%20work%20on%20her%20idea.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20my%20heart%2C%20it%20was%20more%20like%20a%20project%20for%20me%20and%20I%20had%20never%20thought%20of%20becoming%20a%20social%20entrepreneur.%20After%20it%20was%20incubated%20at%20NSRCEL%20(Nadathur%20S.%20Raghavan%20Centre%20for%20Entrepreneurial%20Learning)%2C%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Management%2C%20Bengaluru%2C%20I%20realised%20this%20initiative%20had%20much%20more%20potential%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFoundation%20for%20Social%20Town%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20non-profit%20organisation%20was%20started%20with%20500%20people%20and%20has%20engaged%20more%20than%206%2C000%20people%20in%20social%20work.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20initially%20used%20WhatsApp%20groups%20and%20emails%20for%20interactions.%20We%20used%20the%20platforms%20to%20dissipate%20important%20information%20about%20policy%20changes%2C%20incubation%20programmes%2C%20and%20more%20with%20the%20members%20of%20the%20group%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EThe%20organisation%20does%20not%20charge%20any%20fee%20for%20membership%20and%20is%20open%20for%20anyone%20who%20wants%20to%20bring%20social%20change.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20more%20like%20a%20community%20of%20people%20with%20a%20similar%20school%20of%20thought%20who%20want%20to%20bring%20some%20kind%20of%20change%20in%20the%20society%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20how%20the%20organisation%20works%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CFor%20instance%2C%20if%20there%20is%20a%20changemaker%20in%20Kerala%20who%20wants%20to%20help%20a%20dying%20school%20and%20wants%20to%20give%20them%20computer%20systems%20but%20is%20unsure%20of%20which%20companies%20to%20approach%20and%20how%20to%20raise%20the%20funds%2C%20then%20that%20is%20where%20Social%20Town%20steps%20in.%20We%20try%20to%20connect%20them%20with%20the%20right%20people%20and%20help%20them%20raise%20resources.%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAkber%20Ali%2C%20a%20social%20worker%20who%20works%20with%20the%20tribals%20of%20Wayanad%2C%20points%20out%20the%20importance%20of%20initiatives%20like%20Social%20Town.%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20worked%20with%20the%20organisation%20many%20times%20now.%20First%20when%20there%20was%20a%20flood%20back%20in%202019%2C%20then%20during%20a%20landslide%20and%20then%20again%20during%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic.%20When%20you%20work%20in%20remote%20tribal%20areas%2C%20it%20becomes%20very%20difficult%20for%20us%20to%20reach%20out%20to%20people%20in%20cities%20and%20get%20help.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9CNeenu%2C%20during%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%2C%20was%20the%20first%20person%20I%20contacted%20to%20help%20us.%20In%20the%20hills%2C%20it%20was%20very%20difficult%20to%20get%20basic%20hand%20sanitisers%2C%20she%20was%20the%20one%20who%20raised%20the%20money%2C%20collected%20the%20required%20amenities%2C%20and%20sent%20it%20to%20us.%20Once%2C%20it%20was%20known%20to%20other%20people%20that%20we%20needed%20help%2C%20many%20came%20to%20our%20rescue%20but%20it%20was%20the%20initial%20first%20step%20to%20connect%20with%20the%20right%20people%20that%20the%20organisation%20helped%20us%20with.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsocial-town-3-1718888676.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22If%20you%20want%20to%20start%20your%20social%20work%20journey%2C%20Social%20Town%20can%20help!%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsocial-town-3-1718888676.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsocial-town-3-1718888676-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsocial-town-3-1718888676-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsocial-town-3-1718888676-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsocial-town-3-1718888676-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-353678%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EIf%20you%20want%20to%20start%20your%20social%20work%20journey%2C%20Social%20Town%20can%20help!%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20she%20also%20helps%20volunteers%20connect%20with%20the%20right%20organisations%20to%20kickstart%20their%20social%20work%20journey.%20%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReflecting%20on%20her%20social%20work%20journey%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CNo%20matter%20who%20you%20are%20%E2%80%94%20a%20student%2C%20homemaker%2C%20doctor%2C%20or%20architect%20%E2%80%94%20you%20can%20create%20a%20significant%20impact%20on%20society.%20It%20starts%20with%20the%20desire%20to%20make%20a%20difference%20and%20take%20the%20first%20step.%20Mother%20Teresa%20said%20that%20we%20might%20feel%20like%20just%20a%20drop%20in%20the%20ocean%2C%20but%20without%20that%20drop%2C%20the%20ocean%20would%20be%20less.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CFrom%20my%20experience%20as%20a%20volunteer%20to%20starting%20impactful%20projects%2C%20I%E2%80%99ve%20seen%20how%20small%20actions%20can%20create%20big%20waves.%20Volunteer%2C%20work%20together%2C%20and%20be%20that%20crucial%20drop%20in%20the%20ocean%E2%80%94because%20together%2C%20we%20can%20create%20endless%20possibilities.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIf%20you%20are%20a%20changemaker%20looking%20for%20support%20or%20want%20to%20volunteer%2C%20you%20can%20reach%20out%20to%20Neenu%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fthesocialtown.in%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Ehere%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3B%20All%20Pictures%20Credit%3A%20Social%20Town)%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718890771000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsocial-town-1-1718888498.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D353629%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Neenu%20Rathin%20was%20a%20homemaker%20searching%20for%20a%20deeper%20purpose%20in%20life.%20Only%20when%20she%20started%20volunteering%20did%20she%20discover%20her%20passion%20for%20social%20work.%20But%2C%20finding%20credible%20sources%20was%20easier%20said%20than%20done.%20So%20she%20went%20out%20to%20find%20a%20solution.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Tina%20Freese%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A13%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F353629%2Fsocial-work-volunteer-for-ngo-social-town-helps-changemakers-raise-money-neenu-rathin%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Snapchat%20Inc.%20To%20Settle%20Lawsuit%20That%20Claims%20Discrimination%20Against%20Female%20Employees%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22Snapchat%20Inc.%20will%20pay%20%2415%20million%20to%20settle%20a%20lawsuit%20brought%20by%20California%E2%80%99s%20civil%20rights%20agency.%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718878444000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fimg.huffingtonpost.com%2Fasset%2F6673ff00250000b826343082.jpeg%3Fops%3D1200_630%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.huffpost.com%2Fentry%2Fcalifornia-snapchat-discrimination-settlement_n_6673fefce4b069d92e24426f%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Snapchat%20Inc.%20will%20pay%20%2415%20million%20to%20settle%20a%20lawsuit%20brought%20by%20California%E2%80%99s%20civil%20rights%20agency.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.huffpost.com%2Fentry%2Fcalifornia-snapchat-discrimination-settlement_n_6673fefce4b069d92e24426f%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-huffpost-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.huffpost.com%2Fentry%2Fcalifornia-snapchat-discrimination-settlement_n_6673fefce4b069d92e24426f%2Famp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.huffpost.com%2Fentry%2Fcalifornia-snapchat-discrimination-settlement_n_6673fefce4b069d92e24426f%2Famp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20To%20Convert%20100%25%20Greywater%20in%20Your%20Home%20Into%20Usable%20Water%3F%20Start%20With%20This%20Man%E2%80%99s%20Low-Cost%20Idea%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20face%20of%20a%20daunting%20water%20scarcity%2C%20India%2C%20poised%20to%20host%20a%20population%20nearing%20150%20crores%2C%20finds%20itself%20challenged%20with%20rapidly%20depleting%20water%20resources%2C%20particularly%20groundwater.%20The%20latest%20examples%20of%20acute%20water%20shortages%20are%20in%20cities%20like%20Bengaluru%20where%202024%20has%20been%20the%20driest%20month%20so%20far.%20As%20per%20a%20%3Cem%3EBangalore%20Mirror%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%2C%20%E2%80%9CMore%20than%20half%20of%20Bengaluru%E2%80%99s%20borewells%20have%20dried%20up.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESubhajit%20Mukherjee%2C%20a%20green%20activist%20and%20the%20founder%20of%20Mission%20Green%20Mumbai%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20groundwater%20levels%20have%20seen%20a%20staggering%20decrease%20largely%20due%20to%20the%20disappearance%20of%20lakes%20nationwide.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20quality%20and%20quantity%20of%20available%20drinking%20water%20dwindles%2C%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20rallies%20behind%20initiatives%20like%20the%20Jal%20Jivan%20Mission%2C%20stressing%20the%20critical%20need%20for%20water%20conservation%20through%20reuse.%20However%2C%20the%20question%20of%20whether%20only%20institutional%20efforts%20can%20remedy%20the%20issue%20dwindles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20reached%20out%20to%20the%20green%20activist%2C%20earlier%20known%20for%20his%20innovative%20methods%20to%20harvest%20rainwater%2C%20to%20understand%20the%20nuances%20of%20water%20scarcity%20in%20India%20and%20how%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F351304%2Fchennai-bengaluru-water-crisis-prashant-sharma-grey-water-recycling-in-schools%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eone%20can%20use%20greywater%20%3C%2Fa%3Ein%20daily%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhat%20is%20greywater%20and%20why%20reuse%20it%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20heart%20of%20the%20issue%20of%20water%20shortage%20lies%20in%20the%20disproportionate%20use%20of%20potable%20water%20%E2%80%94%20a%20staggering%2098%20percent%20of%20water%20supplied%20to%20Indian%20homes%20is%20used%20for%20purposes%20other%20than%20drinking%20and%20cooking.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20should%20understand%20that%20only%20two%20percent%20of%20the%20water%20supplied%20to%20our%20homes%20is%20used%20for%20drinking%20and%20cooking.%20The%20remaining%2098%20percent%2C%20used%20for%20non-drinking%20purposes%2C%20can%20always%20be%20catered%20to%20through%20recycled%20and%20filtered%20water%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20points%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20urban%20habits%2C%20such%20as%20using%20fresh%20water%20for%20toilet%20flushing%2C%20contribute%20extensively%20to%20water%20wastage.%20%E2%80%9CFlushing%20alone%20gulps%20down%2035%20percent%20of%20a%20typical%20household%E2%80%99s%20water%20consumption%2C%20prompting%20experts%20to%2