gcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESubhajit%20Mukherjee%20has%20been%20advocating%20reusing%20greywater%20and%20is%20also%20the%20founder%20of%20Mission%20Green%20Mumbai.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20why%20recycled%20water%20can%20be%20a%20viable%20option%20for%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F123663%2Fwater-conservation-kadbanwadi%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20water%20conservation%2C%20%3C%2Fa%3Ehe%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CFor%20non-drinking%20purposes%2C%20such%20as%20mopping%20the%20floor%20or%20flushing%20toilets%2C%20where%20there%20is%20no%20direct%20personal%20contact%20with%20the%20water%2C%20using%20recycled%20greywater%20is%20a%20viable%20option%20that%20requires%20minimal%20effort.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecycled%20greywater%20is%20safe%20for%20use%20as%20it%20does%20not%20involve%20direct%20contact%20with%20the%20human%20body%20nor%20is%20it%20used%20for%20consumption%2C%20hence%20not%20affecting%20our%20physical%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSpecial%20emphasis%20should%20be%20placed%20on%20toilet%20flushing%2C%20as%20in%20most%20urban%20areas%2C%2035%25%20of%20the%20freshwater%20supplied%20by%20the%20piped%20water%20system%20is%20wasted%20on%20flushing%20toilets%20every%20day.%20If%20we%20replace%20that%20with%20greywater%2C%20at%20least%2035%20percent%20fresh%20water%20will%20be%20saved%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20notes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESetting%20up%20such%20systems%2C%20contrary%20to%20public%20scepticism%20about%20cost%20and%20complexity%2C%20proves%20neither%20difficult%20to%20install%20nor%20expensive%2C%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20basic%20home%20setup%20for%20recycling%201%2C000%20litres%20of%20greywater%20can%20be%20established%20with%20an%20initial%20investment%20of%20approximately%20Rs%2010%2C000.%20Moreover%2C%20larger%20facilities%20like%20housing%20complexes%20or%20educational%20insti