0products%20available%20in%20more%20than%2060%20countries%20and%20became%20the%20sole%20supplier%20of%20western%20desserts%20to%20most%20weddings%20in%20the%20entire%20North%20India.%20The%20company%E2%80%99s%20annual%20turnover%20stands%20at%20Rs%207%2C000%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20Rajni%20was%20honoured%20with%20the%20Padma%20Shri%20%E2%80%94%20India%E2%80%99s%20fourth-highest%20civilian%20award%20%E2%80%94%20becoming%20an%20inspiration%20for%20millions%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F268130%2Faruns-bakery-delhi-organic-cakes-breads-order-free-surgery%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIndian%20women%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewho%20dream%20of%20becoming%20entrepreneurs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWatch%20her%20inspiring%20story%20here%3A%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-youtube%20wp-embed-aspect-16-9%20wp-has-aspect-ratio%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%20data-origheight%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20data-epautoplay%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20data-facadesrc%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F-BPQ8rrksi0%3Fenablejsapi%3D1%26amp%3Bautoplay%3D0%26amp%3Bcc_load_policy%3D0%26amp%3Bcc_lang_pref%3D%26amp%3Biv_load_policy%3D3%26amp%3Bloop%3D0%26amp%3Bmodestbranding%3D0%26amp%3Brel%3D0%26amp%3Bfs%3D1%26amp%3Bplaysinline%3D1%26amp%3Bautohide%3D2%26amp%3Btheme%3Ddark%26amp%3Bcolor%3Dred%26amp%3Bcontrols%3D1%26amp%3B%5C%22%20data-origwidth%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20data-spai-excluded%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2F-BPQ8rrksi0%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22YouTube%20player%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EPhoto%20credit%3A%20Cremica.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1